name: Amrit Mahotsav: Ek Unmukt Yatra (Run Event, Female)
description:
The Adventure Sports Club of IIT Kanpur brings to you Amritmahotsav: Ek Unmukt Yatra, an event covered under the Government of India initiative, Azadi ka Amrit Mahotsav to commemorate 75 years of independence of India.

It is a run or walk event, where each participant will be expected to cover a distance of 75 km through running over 18 days. The event starts on 29th July.

This club is for the running  female participants only

Please join the whatsapp group below to get updates on events
